Package: DroughtIndices
Type: Package
Title: Drought Indices Calculation Using Remote Sensing Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Muhammad Qasim <mqasim@uni-muenster.de>
Maintainer: Muhammad Qasim <mqasim@uni-muenster.de>
Description: This package calculates various drought indices such as NDVI, VCI, TCI, PCI, and SDCI using remote sensing data. It provides tools for reading input rasters, computing indices, and exporting results. The package includes a vignette that demonstrates the usage of these functions using the Banadir and Shabelle regions of Somalia as a case study.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    raster,
    rasterVis
Suggests:
